Here are the instructions to install Sublime text 2 onto Ubuntu
(Taken from: http://www.codeproject.com/Articles/582849/InstallingplusSublimeplusTextplus2plusonplusLinuxp)

Add the Sublime Text 2 Repository to your Synaptic Package Manager:
	sudo add-apt-repository ppa:webupd8team/sublime-text-2

Update:
	sudo apt-get update

Install Sublime Text:
	sudo apt-get install sublime-text
